{
  "id": "612a4c1505bccd00237f95c0",
  "title": "Open Graph Image as a Service",
  "created": 1630161942,
  "updated": 1630215126,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "612a4c1505bccd00237f95c0",
      "text": "Open Graph Image as a Service",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630161942,
      "updated": 1630161942
    },
    {
      "id": "612a4c21aff09e000023bbee",
      "text": "https://og-image.vercel.app/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630161953,
      "updated": 1630161953
    },
    {
      "id": "612a4c21aff09e000023bbf0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630161954,
      "updated": 1630161954
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c10aff09e000023bbf2",
      "text": "PuppeteerにHTMLを渡してスクリーンショットを撮っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211088,
      "updated": 1630211118
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c2daff09e000023bbf3",
      "text": "\tそのHTMLがFirestoreにアクセスしてデータを読んで描画するのを待たないといけない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211118,
      "updated": 1630211126
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c95aff09e000023bbf7",
      "text": "\tFirestoreへのアクセスがロード後に非同期で走るわけなのでそれを待つ手段が...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211222,
      "updated": 1630211224
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c35aff09e000023bbf4",
      "text": "\t\thttps://pptr.dev/#?product=Puppeteer&version=v10.2.0&show=api-pagesetcontenthtml-options",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211126,
      "updated": 1630211225
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c8aaff09e000023bbf6",
      "text": "\t\t\tPuppeteer側のオプションでネットワーク接続が全部止まるまで待つことができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211210,
      "updated": 1630211225
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0c7eaff09e000023bbf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211198,
      "updated": 1630211198
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0d96aff09e000060f378",
      "text": "　文字列としてHTMLを生成して、setContentしてる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211479,
      "updated": 1630211641
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0e39aff09e000060f37a",
      "text": "　　これはKozanebaと繋ぐの大変そう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211641,
      "updated": 1630211700
    },
    {
      "id": "612b0ecbaff09e000060f37b",
      "text": "　　サービスとして分離してgotoでやるのが良さそう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630211791,
      "updated": 1630211807
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1101aff09e000060f37c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630212355,
      "updated": 1630212355
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1b9daff09e000023bc05",
      "text": "\tページのmetaタグをページロード後にJSで書き換えるような構成にしても各種SNSのクローラーは対応できない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630215070,
      "updated": 1630215112
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1bc8aff09e000023bc0b",
      "text": "\tサーバサイドでHTMLを出しわけないといけない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630215112,
      "updated": 1630215125
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1baeaff09e000023bc0a",
      "text": "\t個別のmetaのついた最小限のHTMLをサーバサイドで作って吐くところまでvercelでやればいいか…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630215087,
      "updated": 1630215126
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1b9daff09e000023bc06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630215070,
      "updated": 1630215070
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1101aff09e000060f37d",
      "text": "キャッシュコントロール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630212355,
      "updated": 1630215026
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1b99aff09e000023bc04",
      "text": "\thttps://vercel.com/docs/edge-network/caching",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630215066,
      "updated": 1630215069
    },
    {
      "id": "612b1109aff09e000060f37e",
      "text": "\thttps://vercel.com/docs/serverless-functions/edge-caching",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630212362,
      "updated": 1630215028
    },
